# Git only — never Lovable agent edits

Focus FinTax Hub is developed **only through this Git repo** (branch → PR → merge).

## Never

- Do **not** call Lovable `send_message` (or any Lovable agent edit) to change product code.
- Do **not** “fix in Lovable and skip the PR.”
- Do **not** treat Lovable chat as the source of truth for diffs.

## Always

- Edit files locally in this workspace.
- Open a GitHub PR for reviewable changes.
- Use Lovable only for **read-only** checks if needed (preview URL, deploy status) — and prefer not using Lovable MCP at all unless the user asks to **publish/deploy** after a merge.

If production is out of sync with `main`, fix it by pushing/merging Git and then deploying — not by re-implementing in the Lovable agent.
